            "content": "\\[\nQ F T \\left| j _ {1} j _ {2} \\dots j _ {n} \\right\\rangle = \\frac {1}{2 ^ {\\frac {n}{2}}} \\left(\\left| 0 \\right\\rangle + e ^ {2 \\pi i 0. j _ {n}} | 1 \\rangle\\right) \\left(\\left| 0 \\right\\rangle + e ^ {2 \\pi i 0. j _ {n - 1} j _ {n}} | 1 \\rangle\\right) \\dots \\left(\\left| 0 \\right\\rangle + e ^ {2 \\pi i 0. j _ {1} \\dots j _ {n}} | 1 \\rangle\\right) \\tag {20.7}\n\\]"
